Name: Traffic Racing
About the game: You can choose one of the fastest cars which suits you best, acceleration and brake capabilities. You can get more credits and scores as long as you do not make accident along challenging highway, then you can use this credits to get new cars and modify them. You are on the freeway, like a mad racer, overtake other cars to score points for a new car, pick up coins, drive as much distance as possible to survive, use a magnet to attract objects, or pick up super acceleration to score points as soon as possible. Traffic Racing is a 3D car simulator, you play as the racer Ron, on the highway, overtake as many cars as possible, and do not get off the highway Game Features: - You can choose different highways. - a large selection of cars
